To run app
- unzip downloaded file
- make minecraftClone-linux file executable:
    - in file explorer or
    - in game directory run: chmod +x minecraftClone-linux
- in game directory run: ./minecraftClone-linux 
- wait for world to generate

How to play:
- classic wasd movement
- mouse control
- left click: destroy block
- right click: place block
- space: free mouse from window
- enter: trap mouse in window
- f: toggle fly mode
- esc: exit game

! THANKS FOR DOWNLOAD !
